Class BedwarsZeta

All Implemented Interfaces:
CommandExecutor, TabCompleter, TabExecutor, Plugin
public class BedwarsZeta extends ZetaPlugin
BedwarsZeta main class. Contains all instances of DataStorers as well as many helpful utility methods. This is a ZetaPlugin, a custom extension to the normal JavaPlugin
Author:
YeetManLord
Plugin Usage:
Main Class. Usable by other plugins.
